    "body": "minimal example:\n\n``` rust\n#![feature(volatile)]\n\n#[repr(C)]\nstruct X(u64, u64);\n\nfn main() {\n    let mut x = X(0, 0);\n    unsafe { std::ptr::write_volatile(&mut x, X(5, 6)) };\n}\n```\n\non 32-bit systems using a 64-bit type also works. Anything smaller than the word size does not give an error.\n",
